_sText:
This is a very big maze! 
It may be really cool, unfortunately, it may be very boring if there are few people playing. 
I recommend you to create a dm_ server if you wanna play this.
If you don't do that, it may take long time to wait if you get killed.
Associate you with alot of people and play together on a deathmatch server, and make the best of this map that you can;)
Download and test the map with some bots, and you'll find out that it's pretty cool to play also then!

|Morgi5|
